snippet.textDisplay:
I see a lot of people saying "I'm European and this sounds like a cult". Mind you, we have similar student clubs in Europe.

Last year in Belgium a 20 yo drank himself in coma with fish oil during hazing and died. In 2013 in Luik a student drank so much water she went into coma. In 2016 during hazing in Groningen, a guy had to be hospitalized with brain oedema because another guy stood on his head.

So itvisn't just the USA. Also, most studentclubs are totally harmless, it is usually just the one or two that seriously misbehave that give the rest a bad name.
